| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4063 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 529c0b6f-6241-58f4-b9a6-81d6e2cff20b"
